title: KANU nominated Senator Zipporah Kittony says she is retiring from active politics - VIDEO | The Standard
text:
KTN NEWS / 8 hours ago [VIDEO] KANU nominated Senator Zipporah Kittony says she is retiring from active politics 
KANU nominated Senator Zipporah Kittony says she is retiring from active politics. Kittony says she will however continue to support women and children in her private capacity.
